{
  "stem": "23572.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, learn-- learn things-- I think the word means preparation, if I'm-- if I'm correct in-- my-- my Hebrew is not that good.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were-- we were studying Zionism, Jewish history, even some skills, agriculture, you know, to know in case-- if we could reach Palestine, if we are in a kibbutz or yishuv or-- or a moshav-- the different types of moshav-- you know, the kibbutz and the different types of kibbutzim-- and-- and Zionist history, and everything else, among other things.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Plus we tried to get some general education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we set up a [? harasha ?] in-- in the mountains of Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Slovenia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called Lesno Brdo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we had no name for it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we just-- we organized ourselves in the little [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just-- we just made-- made the best of it, you know, tried to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before we know-- things started to get hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What-- what-- what I mean by getting hot-- the Tito Partisans, the Communists, you know, started to get active.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they are-- they are ones, the Italian-- the-- the Italian army-- which was very good to us-- as a matter of fact, there was a time the-- the officers came-- came up with a-- you know, and they wanted to have the music and dance because Professor Boris Jochvidson played the piano.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, they wanted-- you know, wanted-- one of our fellows, he used to sing in the-- in the children's choir of Vienna, so he used to sing Italian operas.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, so this guy has-- nostalgic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to come to us, and they were a little dancing with our girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, we weren't-- they weren't little girls, but young girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
